"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-arts-entertainment-music-news-celine-dion-paris-olympics-stiff-person-syndrome-b2584523.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Olympic opening ceremony would mark Dion's first stage performance since she announced her Stiff Person Syndrome diagnosis in 2022  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.788116554300843e-13, \"text\": \"mark Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Celine Dionis reportedly set to make her big musical comeback at the 2024 ParisOlympicslater this week.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 56-year-old singer is preparing to perform at the opening ceremony on Friday (July 26), according to a report byVariety.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independenthas contacted Dion's representative for comment.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This would mark Dion's first stage performance since 2022 when she canceled her tour andannounced she had been diagnosed with Stiff Person Syndrome(SPS), a rare and incurable neurological condition that often causes muscle stiffness and painful spasms.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.788116554300843e-13, \"text\": \"mark Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8581493181771388, \"rank\": 0.16521741065064566, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Monday (July 22), Dion arrived at the Royal Monceau Hotel near the Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es, where the ceremony's other rumored headliner, Lady Gaga, is staying,Varietyreported.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_Monceau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8176712160444525e-23, \"text\": \"Monceau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_Monceau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parc_Monceau\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"My Heart Will Go On\\\" singer teased a comeback in April, tellingVogue France: \\\"The way I see it, I have two choices.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Either I train like an athlete and work super hard, or I switch off and it's over, I stay at home, listen to my songs, stand in front of my mirror and sing to myself.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have chosen to work with all my body and soul, from head to toe, with a medical team.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be the best I can be.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal is to see the Eiffel Tower again!\\\"\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, Dion released her documentary,I Am: Celine Dion, which provides an honest behind-the-scenes look at her life with SPS.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.8581493181771388, \"rank\": 0.16521741065064566, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the firsttrailer for the heartbreaking documentary, the Grammy-winning artist broke down in tears as she gave a candid account of her struggle with the disorder.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am working hard every day.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have to admit, it's been a struggle,\\\" Dion said in the trailer.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I miss it so much,\\\"she tearfully said of performing.\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The people.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I miss them.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can not run, I will walk.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can not walk, I will crawl.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I will not stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy unlimited access to 100 million ad-free songs 