ey down or one note down.\\\"\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Olympics will commence with a unique opening ceremony along the River Seine before the competition begins on Saturday (July 27) and continues for 16 days.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3304, \"end\": 3315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is the first city to host the summer Games for a third time.\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3395, \"end\": 3400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.863105738558705e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow The Independent's Olympics 2024 live blog here for real-time updates  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3591, \"end\": 3602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1231512043505661e-11, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"